# Sound Effects

## Objective
Implement non-intrusive sound effects for key gamification events.

## Tasks
1. Safely introduce lightweight audio assets (e.g., retro level-up chimes or minor success sounds).
2. Wire audio playback to successful drag-and-drop actions ("Task Done") and level transitions.
3. Provide a global mute toggle for users in office environments.
